import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Wrapper>
        <Title>SIGN IN</Title>
        <Form>
          <Input placeholder="username" />
          <Input placeholder="password" />
          <Button>LOGIN</Button>
          <Link>Forget your password?</Link>
          <Link>Create a new account</Link>
        </Form>
      </Wrapper>
      
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
